首长.note: Standard address for the leaders of the group.

文总.note: Refers to Wen Desi. 'Zong' is short for Zongcai (President) or Zongjingli (General Manager).

马督公.note: Refers to Ma Qianzhu. Nickname implying high supervisory power, akin to the Eastern Depot commanders.

穿越众.note: The group of people who traveled back in time.

宅男.note: Men who stay at home, obsessed with ACG culture. Meaning: Nerd/Homebody.
